This File consists of  ALL Pico Peripheral program:- UART , SPI , I2C , PIO , GPIO ,KEYPAD/

  * UART - uart0 and uar1 are used to  print a statement  and resive user  inpiut .  
  * SPI -  USED For ili9341  - 3.4 TFT SPI 480x320 v1.0  display.another main.c is provided For  MOSI- MISO loopback testing.
  * PIO - USED to  blink an  LED. 
  * GPIO - USED  to Test GPIO LEDS
  * i2c - USED  For lcd display with pcf8574 . 
  * KEYPAD - 4X4 MATRIX keypad.
   
   
